snippet.title: Vultures: Scavengers of Death - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Check out gameplay and some of the terrifying enemies of Vultures: Scavengers of Death in this trailer for the upcoming turn-based survival-horror roguelike game. Vultures: Scavengers of Death is coming to PC in 2025. In Vultures: Scavengers of Death, face zombies and fearsome monsters as you seek the path to recover a valuable artifact. Unravel the history of Salento Valley and its downfall after a bioterrorist attack led by a secret cult involved with the powerful corporation Eugenesys Tech.
